subject: Baseball
Little League World Series
lead_paragraph: David Umphreville, Jr. had a two-run single and Zane Conlon snared a line drive to end a rally as Warner Robins, Ga., won the United States crown and advanced to the Little League World Series final with a 5-2 victory over Lubbock, Tex., yesterday in South Williamsport, Pa.
